{
  "stem": "20609.1",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] and that-- every day my mother and myself, since there was no school, we went to the Jewish community and-- with all the other women and wives and daughters and whatever-- and trying to find out-- we didn't know where my father was.",
      "word_count": 48
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We didn't know at that time how to get him out.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But that's when we went to the Jewish community to find out.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And at one of those-- we went there every day, walking, because we were not allowed to use the street car.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And one lady, downstairs one day-- I am-- it seems like I remember it exactly what happened, today-- said to my mother, she says they're making up a list of 300 children to go to Denmark.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Why don't you put your son's name on the list?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "There were certain requirements.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You couldn't be 15 years old-- not older than 15.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And you had to be, like, from 12 or up to-- it was only like a three year-- well, I-- we went upstairs.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "She put my name down and completely forgot about it.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So a couple of months later-- [DRINKS] this was done sometime in September or October.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I don't know the exact day then.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "All of a sudden, about December or January was, we were notified we were accepted, to get all the papers together.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I needed permission to leave the country.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I needed all kinds of papers.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we did it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We walked around to all these different places, including the police department and the Gestapo.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They had to give permission.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "That was the secret police they had there.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But it wasn't as secret as-- as the name said, you know.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They were-- they were all around.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
